text:
Proud Russia

07 Nov 2019, 19:23

More than 4000 Russian soldiers marched in the capital Moscow. Every year since 2003, the Military Parade commemorates the parade of 1941 on 7 November. Also soldiers of the "Yunarmia", the "young army", marched in this year.
